# 🎓 Student Management System

A complete web-based application built using **Flask, HTML, CSS, and Python** to manage student data efficiently.  
This project demonstrates CRUD operations (Create, Read, Update, Delete) with a clean UI and Flask backend integration.

---

## 🚀 Features

- 🔐 Secure Login and Registration System  
- 🧾 Add, View, Edit, and Delete Student Records  
- 💾 SQLite Database Integration with SQLAlchemy ORM  
- 🎨 Responsive UI using HTML, CSS, and Bootstrap  
- ⚡ Dynamic Templates using Jinja2  
- 💬 Flash Messages and Error Handling  
- 🧠 Clean and Commented Codebase

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

| Category | Technology |
|-----------|-------------|
| **Frontend** | HTML5, CSS3, Bootstrap, JavaScript |
| **Backend** | Python (Flask Framework) |
| **Database** | SQLite (SQLAlchemy ORM) |
| **Server** | Flask Development Server |

